    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="python基础语法"><a href="#python基础语法" class="headerlink" title="python基础语法"></a>python基础语法</h1><h2 id="基础数据类型与变量声明"><a href="#基础数据类型与变量声明" class="headerlink" title="基础数据类型与变量声明"></a>基础数据类型与变量声明</h2><h3 id="变量声明"><a href="#变量声明" class="headerlink" title="变量声明"></a>变量声明</h3><blockquote><p>与Javascript、C、Java等语言不同，python 不用变量声明，直接赋值即可，和Js数据类型相似，具有弱类型特点（建议强化数据类型思维）。建议字符后边都跟一个空格。</p><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">star = <span class="string">&#x27;xingmingwo&#x27;</span> <span class="comment"># 声明一个变量并赋值</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>变量建议采用 ‘_’ 进行连接；函数定义建议采用驼峰式写法：</p><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">star_var = <span class="string">&#x27;xingmingwo&#x27;</span> </span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">def</span> <span class="title">starHome</span>():</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">pass</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></blockquote><h3 id="基础数据类"><a href="#基础数据类" class="headerlink" title="基础数据类"></a>基础数据类</h3><h4 id="string"><a href="#string" class="headerlink" title="string"></a>string</h4><blockquote><p> 字符串类型=&gt;采用 ‘string’, “string”, ‘’’string’’’，以解决标点的嵌套。’’’string’’’ 可以换行表示一个字符串.</p> <figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">xing = <span class="string">&#x27;mingwo&#x27;</span> <span class="comment"># 单引号</span></span><br><span class="line">ming = <span class="string">&quot;xingwo&quot;</span> <span class="comment"># 双引号</span></span><br><span class="line">wo = <span class="string">&#x27;&#x27;&#x27;xingming&#x27;&#x27;&#x27;</span> <span class="comment"># 三引号</span></span><br><span class="line">xing_ming_wo = <span class="string">&#x27;&#x27;&#x27;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">星明窝</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">&#x27;&#x27;&#x27;</span> <span class="comment"># 可进行换行，换行符最终也体现在字符串打印结果</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 引号相互嵌套</span></span><br><span class="line">star = <span class="string">&quot;&#x27;xingmingwo&#x27;&quot;</span> <span class="comment"># print-&gt; &#x27;xingmingwo&#x27;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 字符串中标点可以通过反斜杠 \ 进行转译</span></span><br><span class="line">horn = <span class="string">&#x27;\&#x27;xingmingwo\&#x27;&#x27;</span> <span class="comment"># print-&gt; &#x27;xingmingwo&#x27;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></blockquote><p>各类型通过 str(data) 进行转换为字符串类型，使用type(data)输出数据类型</p><blockquote> <figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">xing = <span class="number">123</span></span><br><span class="line">ming = str(xing) <span class="comment"># print(type(ming))-&gt; string</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></blockquote><h4 id="number"><a href="#number" class="headerlink" title="number"></a>number</h4><p>整型int，long；浮点float</p><blockquote><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 顾名思</span></span><br><span class="line">xiao = <span class="number">10</span></span><br><span class="line">ming = <span class="number">10.1</span></span><br><span class="line">print(type(xiao)) <span class="comment"># -&gt; int</span></span><br><span class="line">print(type(ming)) <span class="comment"># -&gt;float</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># int()将浮点型转换为整形</span></span><br><span class="line">print(type(ming)) <span class="comment"># -&gt; float</span></span><br><span class="line">print(type(int(ming)) <span class="comment"># -&gt; int</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># float()转换为浮点型</span></span><br><span class="line">print(type(xiao)) <span class="comment"># -&gt; int</span></span><br><span class="line">print(type(float(xiao))) <span class="comment"># -&gt; float</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></blockquote><h4 id="boolean"><a href="#boolean" class="headerlink" title="boolean"></a>boolean</h4><p>布尔值 -&gt; 只有两个值：True &lt;&gt; False，注意在python中布尔值开头为<strong>大写</strong>。</p><p>and, or, not 运算</p><blockquote><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">good = <span class="literal">True</span></span><br><span class="line">bad = <span class="literal">False</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># and or not 在if语句中较多运用</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># and 两者为True才True</span></span><br><span class="line">print(good <span class="keyword">and</span> bad) <span class="comment"># -&gt; False  </span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># or 两者为 False 才为False</span></span><br><span class="line">print(good <span class="keyword">or</span> bad) <span class="comment"># -&gt; True</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># not 与原互斥</span></span><br><span class="line">print(<span class="keyword">not</span> bad) <span class="comment"># -&gt; True</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></blockquote><h4 id="None"><a href="#None" class="headerlink" title="None"></a>None</h4><p>空值，注意不是null</p><h2 id="数组与字典"><a href="#数组与字典" class="headerlink" title="数组与字典"></a>数组与字典</h2><h3 id="数组"><a href="#数组" class="headerlink" title="数组"></a>数组</h3><p>数组包括列表与元组。</p><h4 id="列表与元组-and"><a href="#列表与元组-and" class="headerlink" title="列表与元组 [] and {}"></a>列表与元组 [] and {}</h4><p>列表中数据()可变，而元组中数据不可操作</p><blockquote><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br><span class="line">28</span><br><span class="line">29</span><br><span class="line">30</span><br><span class="line">31</span><br><span class="line">32</span><br><span class="line">33</span><br><span class="line">34</span><br><span class="line">35</span><br><span class="line">36</span><br><span class="line">37</span><br><span class="line">38</span><br><span class="line">39</span><br><span class="line">40</span><br><span class="line">41</span><br><span class="line">42</span><br><span class="line">43</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">xing = [<span class="string">&#x27;xing&#x27;</span>, <span class="string">&#x27;ming&#x27;</span>, <span class="string">&#x27;xiao&#x27;</span>] </span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 数组与数据嵌套</span></span><br><span class="line">ming = [<span class="string">&#x27;xing&#x27;</span>, <span class="number">10</span>, <span class="number">10.1</span>, [<span class="string">&#x27;xiao&#x27;</span>, <span class="string">&#x27;ming&#x27;</span>],&#123;<span class="string">&#x27;star&#x27;</span>,<span class="string">&#x27;home&#x27;</span>&#125;]</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 索引 -&gt;从0开始</span></span><br><span class="line">print(xing[<span class="number">0</span>]) <span class="comment">#  -&gt; xing</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 索引: 左闭右开  &lt; ?:xing[-1] -&gt; ?</span></span><br><span class="line">print(xing[<span class="number">0</span>:<span class="number">2</span>]) <span class="comment">#  -&gt; xing ming  </span></span><br><span class="line">print(xing[:]) <span class="comment"># -&gt;xing ming xiao 等价于print(xing)</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 修改列表数据</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 替换 -&gt; variable[index] = contextt</span></span><br><span class="line">xing[<span class="number">2</span>] = <span class="string">&#x27;star&#x27;</span></span><br><span class="line">print(xing) <span class="comment"># -&gt; xing ming star</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 增加 append -&gt; variable.append(context)</span></span><br><span class="line">xing.append(<span class="string">&#x27;xiao&#x27;</span>)</span><br><span class="line">print(xing) <span class="comment"># -&gt; xing ming star xiao</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 删除 delete -&gt; del variable[index]</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">del</span> xing[<span class="number">2</span>] <span class="comment"># star</span></span><br><span class="line">print(xing) <span class="comment"># -&gt; xing ming xiao</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 迭代输出数组 for...in...</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">for</span> key <span class="keyword">in</span> xing:</span><br><span class="line">    print(xing[key])</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 输出：</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># xing</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># ming</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># xiao</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 列表方法</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># len(list) -&gt;返回列表长度</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># max(list),min(list) -&gt; 返回最大,最小值</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># list.count(obj) -&gt;返回列表中obj的个数</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># list.pop(list[index]) -&gt; 移除并返回list[index],list.pop() -&gt; 默认最后一项</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># list.remove(obj) -&gt; 移除列表中obj</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># list.clear() -&gt; 清空</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># list.sort([func]) -&gt; 列表根据func排序</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 注：数组相加等于数组连接</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">#  array1 + array2 </span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 数组与n相乘等于将原列表复制n个然后组合成新的重复n次的数组</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></blockquote><h3 id="字典"><a href="#字典" class="headerlink" title="字典"></a>字典</h3><p>类似于json，有键和值。</p><p>dict = {key1 : value1, key2 : value2, ….}</p><blockquote><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">dict = &#123;<span class="string">&#x27;xing&#x27;</span> : <span class="string">&#x27;星&#x27;</span>,<span class="string">&#x27;ming&#x27;</span> : <span class="string">&#x27;明&#x27;</span>，<span class="string">&#x27;wo&#x27;</span> : <span class="string">&#x27;窝&#x27;</span>&#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 迭代输出 for in</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">for</span> key <span class="keyword">in</span> dict:</span><br><span class="line">    print(key +<span class="string">&#x27;:&#x27;</span> + dict[key])</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># &#x27;xing&#x27; : &#x27;星&#x27;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># &#x27;ming&#x27; : &#x27;明&#x27; </span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># &#x27;wo&#x27; : &#x27;窝&#x27;</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 追加</span></span><br><span class="line">dict[<span class="string">&#x27;home&#x27;</span>] = <span class="string">&#x27;star&#x27;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 删除</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">del</span> dict[<span class="string">&#x27;home&#x27;</span>]</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></blockquote><h2 id="基础语句"><a href="#基础语句" class="headerlink" title="基础语句"></a>基础语句</h2><h4 id="条件语句"><a href="#条件语句" class="headerlink" title="条件语句"></a>条件语句</h4><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># if context: -&gt; context 为True时执行语句内，否则执行else内语句继续下一个</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 任何非 0 和非空（null）值为 True，0 或者 null 为 False</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 判断语句 == &lt;= &gt;= != &gt; &lt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">if</span> <span class="literal">None</span>:</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">pass</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">else</span>:</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">pass</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 多条件判断 if context1:...elif context2:...else: pass</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h4 id="循环语句"><a href="#循环语句" class="headerlink" title="循环语句"></a>循环语句</h4><p>break     在语句块执行过程中终止循环，并且跳出整个循环                 </p><p> continue 在语句块执行过程中终止当前循环，跳出该次循环，执行下一次循环 </p><p> pass      pass 是空语句，是为了保持程序结构的完整性                    </p><blockquote><p>for循环</p><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># for in </span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 数组、字典循环</span></span><br><span class="line">xing = [<span class="string">&#x27;xing&#x27;</span>, <span class="string">&#x27;ming&#x27;</span>, <span class="string">&#x27;wo&#x27;</span>]</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">for</span> key <span class="keyword">in</span> xing:</span><br><span class="line">    print(xing[key])</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># -&gt; xing</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># -&gt; ming</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># -&gt; wo</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 字符串迭代</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">for</span> key <span class="keyword">in</span> <span class="string">&#x27;wo&#x27;</span>:</span><br><span class="line">    print(key)</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># -&gt; w</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># -&gt; o</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># range(s_num,e_num,step) s_num-&gt;开始数值，e_num-&gt;结束数值,step-&gt;步长,默认为1，左闭右开</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">for</span> key <span class="keyword">in</span> range(<span class="number">0</span>,<span class="number">2</span>):</span><br><span class="line">    print(key)</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># -&gt; 0</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># -&gt; 1</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>while循环</p><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># while context: pass</span></span><br><span class="line">num = <span class="number">2</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">while</span> num:</span><br><span class="line">    print(num)</span><br><span class="line">    num --</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># -&gt; 2</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># -&gt; 1</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></blockquote><h4 id="语句嵌套"><a href="#语句嵌套" class="headerlink" title="语句嵌套"></a>语句嵌套</h4><blockquote><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">for</span> key <span class="keyword">in</span> <span class="string">&#x27;xiao&#x27;</span>:</span><br><span class="line">    print(key)</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">if</span> key == <span class="string">&#x27;a&#x27;</span>:</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">continue</span> <span class="comment"># 跳过a</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># -&gt; x</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># -&gt; i</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># -&gt; o</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></blockquote><h2 id="函数"><a href="#函数" class="headerlink" title="函数"></a>函数</h2><p>def function_name():</p><p>​         context</p><blockquote><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">def</span> <span class="title">star</span>():</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">pass</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></blockquote><h2 id="正则表达式"><a href="#正则表达式" class="headerlink" title="正则表达式"></a>正则表达式</h2><h2 id="面向对象"><a href="#面向对象" class="headerlink" title="面向对象"></a>面向对象</h2>]]></content>
    
